      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "OLYMPIA, May 11.-Joint rates\nfor interurban roads with steam\nroad connections is to be provided\nin a new order being framed by\nthe state railroad commission. This\nprovision is made to overcome de-\nfeet in the former joint rate order,\nwhich excluded interurban roads\nand was thereby exposed to attack\nas class legislation."
    }
